Titilope Sonuga,Listen nke a makwaara dị ka Titi Sonuga, bụ onye Naijiria na-ede uri, injinia obodo, na onye na-eme ihe nkiri nke na-etinye oge ya n'etiti Lagos na Edmonton, Canada.Listen (help·info)

Titilope Sonuga, onye amụrụ na Lagos, Nigeria, kwagara na Edmonton, Canada, mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na atọ. Sonuga nọrọ afọ ise na-arụ ọrụ dị ka injinia mgbe ọ na-achụso mmasị ya na uri ma na-eme ihe n'oge ezumike ya.
Sonuga meriri afọ 2011 Canadian Authors Association Emerging Writer Award na afọ 2012 Maya Angelou Poetry Contest. O guzobere Rouge Poetry na Edmonton, usoro uri slam
N'ọnwa Mee afọ 2015 ọ ghọrọ onye na-ede uri mbụ pụtara na emume ncheta onye isi ala Naijiria
O bipụtara nchịkọta uri n'afọ 2016. Sonuga emeela na Ememme abụ abụ Lagos International
A kpọrọ ya onye edemede nke itoolu nke Edmonton.
na 2015 o kwuputara njikọ aka ya na onye na-ese foto Seun Williams. Kemgbe ahụ ọ ghọrọ nne.
